#: ../../../release_details/9.5/transition-from-vtkm-to-viskores.md:1
msgid "Transition from VTKm to Viskores"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/transition-from-vtkm-to-viskores.md:3
msgid ""
"VTK has transitioned its dependency from [VTKm][vtkm] to [Viskores]"
"[viskores]. This transition involves several important changes:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/transition-from-vtkm-to-viskores.md:6
msgid "VTK now depends on Viskores instead of VTKm"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/transition-from-vtkm-to-viskores.md:7
msgid "Fides has been updated to also transition its dependency to Viskores"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/transition-from-vtkm-to-viskores.md:8
msgid ""
"The accelerator vtkm VTK module has been modified to use Viskores in its "
"implementation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/transition-from-vtkm-to-viskores.md:9
msgid "VTK Accelerator VTKm API remains fully compatible for downstream users"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/transition-from-vtkm-to-viskores.md:10
msgid ""
"No code changes should be required for applications using the VTK "
"Accelerator API"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/transition-from-vtkm-to-viskores.md:12
msgid "Build Breaking Change"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/transition-from-vtkm-to-viskores.md:14
msgid ""
"The flag `VTK_ENABLE_VISKORES_OVERRIDES` has been introduced * This new flag "
"deprecates the previous `VTK_ENABLE_VTKM_OVERRIDES`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/transition-from-vtkm-to-viskores.md:16
msgid ""
"Projects using the previous flag in their build system will need to update "
"accordingly"
msgstr ""
